       fhir:Extension.valueMarkdown [ fhir:value "For Ty21a, a 3-dose oral immunization schedule, administering the vaccine every second \n  (alternate) day, is recommended above 6 years of age. If interruption between doses is > 21 days, restart primary series." ]
