       fhir:Extension.valueMarkdown [ fhir:value "Revaccination is recommended every 3–7 years for Ty21a (every 1 to 7 years for travellers from non-endemic \n  to endemic areas, depending on national policies). As a general rule, any live vaccine may be given either simultaneously \n  or at an interval of 4 weeks." ]
